        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Introducing John Austin, who visits St Louis.
</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>Texas </placeName><date when="1828-05-10">May 10. 1828</date></p>
<p>My Dear <persName>Brother </persName>and <persName>Sister</persName>,</p>

<p>This will be handed to you by <persName>Mr. John Austin</persName> a relative of ours,
he has business in <placeName>St Louis </placeName>and has promised to call at the <placeName>mines</placeName>
and see you&#8212;his stay probably will be very short, tho. long enough
to give him time to answer your enquiries relative to this <placeName>country</placeName></p>

<p><persName>John </persName>has been with me several years in this <placeName>country</placeName>, he is a truly
worthy man and you must make him as comfortable as you can while
with you&#8212;</p>

<p>I wrote you a short time ago and have nothing particular to say
since&#8212;<persName>Brother </persName>will write you from <placeName>Orleans</placeName></p>

<p><persName>S. F. Austin </persName>   [Rubric]</p>



        </div1>
    </body>
